    "text_with_icons_4UkBa4": {
      "type": "text-with-icons",
      "blocks": {
        "item_6JVnrN": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "picto-coupon",
            "custom_icon": "shopify://shop_images/1_d408c90c-ec99-457f-afeb-89f366155bb1.png",
            "mobile_icon_width": 120,
            "icon_width": 120,
            "icon_background_type": "circle",
            "icon_background": "",
            "icon_color": "#343a40",
            "title": "Retail",
            "content": "<p>We are the <strong>leading baby and toddler cutlery brand</strong> in the UK. With the global tableware sector identified for <strong>substantial growth</strong> in the next few years we are perfectly placed to help you capitalise.  Find out more about the benefits of doddl:</p><ul><li>Our products are <strong>innovative and solve problems</strong> like no other brand on the market</li><li>Our<strong> customers invest more </strong>in our products because of the benefits they deliver</li><li>Our products recieve <strong>very high referral rates</strong></li><li><strong>Our customer base is vast, </strong>mums, dads, grandparents, carers, family members and friends</li><li>Our products are <strong>5-star rated </strong>and <strong>recommended by child feeding, development and nutritional experts</strong></li></ul><p></p>"
          }
        },
        "item_4eNACU": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "picto-coupon",
            "custom_icon": "shopify://shop_images/3.png",
            "mobile_icon_width": 120,
            "icon_width": 120,
            "icon_background_type": "circle",
            "icon_background": "",
            "icon_color": "#301562",
            "title": "Early Years Education",
            "content": "<p><strong>Enhancing learning and success at mealtimes.</strong></p><p>At doddl we don't cut corners with our products. <strong>Thoroughly researched and rigorously tested, </strong>doddl products are multiple award winning and certified safe. With doddl you can rest assured that you are offering the children in your care the <strong>very best quality products </strong>that offer clear benefits. Find out more:</p><ul><li><strong>Enhanced learning</strong> and skill development</li><li><strong>Easier, more successful </strong>mealtimes</li><li><strong>More eating and less waste</strong></li><li>High quality, long lasting and <strong>dishwasher safe</strong></li><li>Recommended by parents of children with <strong>SEN</strong></li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "item_RGDwdz": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "picto-coupon",
            "custom_icon": "shopify://shop_images/2_919faa2b-8626-4b2c-a5d7-d0dfa2d5ebde.png",
            "mobile_icon_width": 120,
            "icon_width": 120,
            "icon_background_type": "circle",
            "icon_background": "#eaeaea",
            "icon_color": "#301562",
            "title": "Hospitality",
            "content": "<p><strong>Elevate your dining experience.</strong></p><p>Create an <strong>exceptional experience</strong> for your young patrons and their families by introducing our expertly designed products for babies and toddlers. Enhance<strong> your dining establishment's family-friendly reputation</strong> while satisfying parents and captivating young diners.</p><p>Find out more about the proven benefits of doddl:</p><ul><li><strong>Less mess</strong> and clear-up time</li><li><strong>Calmer </strong>eating environment</li><li><strong>Long-lasting</strong>, high quality and dishwasher safe</li><li><strong>Added value</strong> and point of difference to your competitors</li></ul>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
