    "media_with_text_EDMkE8": {
      "type": "media-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "image_GmrFyB": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/doddl_unedited_LR4256_LR.jpg",
            "media_width": 50,
            "media_position": "start",
            "text_position": "place-self-center text-center",
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 48,
            "subheading": "",
            "title": "The impact of doddl",
            "content": "<p><strong>Matthew Siadatan - Balihoo Restaurant</strong><br/><br/>\"At Ballihoo, we aim to offer the best service possible, and as we are family led, we try and heighten even the tiniest of toddler's experiences. We all have moments when we come across <strong>something we get really excited about.</strong> The inclusion of doddl has done that for our little people at Lower Mill Estate.</p><p>The cutlery is very clever, sleek and sophisticated, so it elevates our little guests' food journey and the mum's and dad's love it too.</p><p>The nature of the cutlery and plates <strong>brings calmness, education and elegance</strong> to the table and the difference it has made to eating time is clearly apparent. Its very durable too, so it is proving to withstand the wear and tear of a busy restaurant. </p><p>It's versatility is great, and can be used over starters, mains and desserts, and also very easy to clean and polish!\"</p>",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "background": "#fbfbfb",
            "background_gradient": "",
            "text_color": "#1a1a1a",
            "text_gradient": "",
            "button_background": "",
            "button_text_color": ""
          }
        },
        "image_rBM7cB": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Coigne_post.png",
            "media_width": 50,
            "media_position": "end",
            "text_position": "place-self-center text-center",
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 96,
            "subheading": "The Coigne Nursery",
            "title": "",
            "content": "<p>\"A big shout out to doddl cutlery. As many of you know, the Coigne children love using doddl cutlery and <strong>as practitioners we have seen some amazing results</strong> in independence at lunchtime and snack time, as well as with their fine motorskills.\"</p>",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "background": "#fbfbfb",
            "background_gradient": "",
            "text_color": "#212529",
            "text_gradient": "",
            "button_background": "",
            "button_text_color": ""
          }
        },
        "image_M6MbpC": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/thumbnail_PHOTO-2023-08-08-20-54-58_a3d24b32-7584-47d9-8f78-c2d8c040cb2d.jpg",
            "media_width": 50,
            "media_position": "start",
            "text_position": "place-self-center text-center",
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 48,
            "subheading": "Forest Green Rovers (FGR)",
            "title": "",
            "content": "<p>“doddl provides a solution for the younger guests in hospitality areas at The New Lawn, as most parents know mealtimes can be stressful. doddl is providing cutlery that is the right-size and easy for the children to use, <strong>this means that the families are having a positive experience </strong>and children<strong> </strong>are enjoying using the products. It makes sense to offer doddl as we are a family-friendly club that encourages education, food is a key part of a child’s life, <strong>if they enjoy eating the food here at FGR then they will return with their families.</strong> This also helps with the development of their personal skills.”</p>",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "background": "#fbfbfb",
            "background_gradient": "",
            "text_color": "#212529",
            "text_gradient": "",
            "button_background": "",
            "button_text_color": ""
          }
        },
        "image_QjPEkH": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Happy_boy_and_dad_aqua.jpg",
            "media_width": 50,
            "media_position": "start",
            "text_position": "place-self-center text-center",
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 48,
            "subheading": "",
            "title": "Customer reviews",
            "content": "<p><strong>\"It was like magic?!</strong> He managed to pick the loaded spoon up comfortably and eat. I was amazed at how well he did. Thank you for a great product. Have recommended to friends.\" Hannah<br/><br/>\"My 18 month old finds holding this cutlery much easier. Shes more confident in self feeding. <strong>Well made and worth every penny!\" </strong>Laura<br/><br/>\"These sets are brilliant. My 16 month old son is <strong>so much better at using cutlery</strong> himself. We bought the bowl also and it does not move. Really worth the money!\"  Charlotte</p>",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "background": "#fbfbfb",
            "background_gradient": "",
            "text_color": "#212529",
            "text_gradient": "",
            "button_background": "",
            "button_text_color": ""
          }
        }
