    "faq_c4UB8k": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "item_9K3B8w": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Where do you supply from?",
            "content": "<p>We have complete fulfilment operations established in China, US & UK. Our fulfillment operations allow us to offer partners a flexible approach to supply, to ensure they can work in the most efficient way. We are currently establishing a new Fulfilment Operation within mainland Europe details of which we hope to be confirming shortly.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_JNCVWD": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Do you offer market exclusivity arrangements for Distributors?",
            "content": "<p>Yes, we do. We are very proud of how we work with partners to create a Market Entry Plan and market exclusivity rights will be reviewed as part of this process.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_ExhYfj": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Do you provide Marketing Support to partners?",
            "content": "<p>As a doddl partner, you will have full access to the doddl marketing asset shared drive, where you will find everything you will need to support the growth of the brand in your market. Assets are editable so that you can localise them for your market. In addition, we also share assets created by partners that have performed well in the local market.</p><p>As a doddl partner, you will also be able to share your ideas for required assets with the doddl marketing team who will, where possible, provide the support you require.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_kXK8mc": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How will I keep up to speed with the world of doddl?",
            "content": "<p>As a doddl partner, you will work with one of the doddl team who will help support the growth of the brand in your market. You will meet regularly and receive updates about initiatives taken by the brand and partners across the globe. We will work with you to support any opportunities you identify to grow the brand within your market.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
